		<td><b>Minimum amount of storage space a flash cart should have.</b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />How much and why? I myself think 2MB, as many many projects that are easy enough to bring to NES would needs the graphics space. Pokemon is one good example, lots of images and data there. What do you think?
<br />
<br />Extra:Minimum supported WRAM? Mine is 32KB. 128KB would be very nice, though.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

