		<td><b></b></td>
	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />2MB would be cool to have, but I don't think it's the minimum. With 512/512 it should be possible to do everything we consider "typical NES". 2MB would be more for new ideas and experiments, which I'm all for.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


